-- Toyota U.S. sales down 4.5 percent
-- 
-- Thu May 1, 2008 1:20pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/01/us-toyota-sales-idUSN0138289120080501

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Toyota Motor Co ( 7203.T ) on Thursday reported a 4.5 percent fall in April U.S. auto sales to 217,700 vehicles after adjusting for two more selling days in the month compared with the same month a year earlier. 

 Toyota said its Toyota-brand sales were down 2.7 percent. Sales for its luxury Lexus brand fell 17.1 percent. April had 26 selling days compared with 24 a year earlier. (Reporting by  Soyoung Kim ; editing by John Wallace)